dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Mark Butler. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Stephanie! Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification?
Sure, it's five six one two three four.
Great, thank you. And could you also confirm the make and model of your vehicle?
It's a two zero one nine Honda Civic.
Thank you for the information, Stephanie. Is there anything specific you'd like to discuss or inquire about today?
I wanted to check on the status of a claim I filed last week.
Of course, I can assist you with that. Thank you for your time, Stephanie. I will look into your claim status and provide you with an update as soon as possible. Have a great day!
